{"name":"Dragonstone","type":"feat","effects":[],"system":{"description":{"gm":"","value":"<p>When you are born or created, you are gifted a mystical orb or stone called a Dragonstone. This stone can be used as a spellcasting focus and has light bulk. There may come a time in your life where you lose your dragonstone. If your dragonstone is not on your person, you may take another gifted to you or looted from a slain Divine Dragon. You may change your Heritage by attuning your soul into this new Dragonstone. Doing so takes 10 days to perform safely. However in some times of dire need you can do this process forcefully in 1 hour but will consequently suffer being @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.4D2KBtexWXa6oUMR]{Drained 2}. This drain is reduced by 1 for every 9 levels you have.</p>"},"source":{"value":""},"rules":[],"slug":null,"schema":{"version":0.84,"lastMigration":null},"level":{"value":0},"traits":{"value":[],"rarity":"common"},"category":"ancestryfeature","onlyLevel1":false,"maxTakable":1,"actionType":{"value":"passive"},"actions":{"value":null},"prerequisites":{"value":[]},"location":null},"img":"systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/feat.svg","ownership":{"default":0,"XV70kTufyit7bW3z":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.0f1NF3eZ0RYPU0ab"}},"_stats":{"systemId":"pf2e","systemVersion":"4.12.9","coreVersion":"10.310","createdTime":1703308453468,"modifiedTime":1703319713239,"lastModifiedBy":"XV70kTufyit7bW3z"},"folder":null,"sort":0,"_id":"JAYcq6CmO6mVqblk"}
